Package: knitrtools
Title: Tools to simplify writing knitr documents.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("John", "Didion", email = "code@didion.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to handle common tasks
	performed when writing knitr documents, such as formatting
	numbers and percentages, and referencing figures and tables
	from within the text.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), knitr
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: knitr, kfigr
LazyData: true
